.Dd 1 August 2008
.Os Python 2.x
.Dt CBANK 7 USD
.Sh NAME
.Nm cbank-new-charge
.Nd clusterbank command-line interface
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl u , -user Ar user
.Op Fl r , -resource Ar resource
.Op Fl m , -comment Ar message
.Ar project
.Ar amount
.Sh DESCRIPTION
Charge an
.Ar amount
of a resource to a
.Ar project .
.Pp
Available options:
.Bl -tag
.It Fl u , -user
Specify an associated
.Ar user .
.It Fl r , -resource
Specify which resource to charge. (default specified in
.Pa /etc/clusterbank.conf )
.It Fl m , -comment
Supply an informative message.
.El
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag
.It /etc/clusterbank.conf
Global configuration and defaults.
.El
